<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global                          " table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>u_load_service_catalog</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>true</execute_function><filter_condition table="u_load_service_catalog">u_state=Pending^u_sub_stateVALCHANGES^EQ<item endquery="false" field="u_state" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="Pending"/><item endquery="false" field="u_sub_state" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="VALCHANGES" or="false" value=""/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><message/><name>Load Next Service Catalog Element</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[function onAfter(current, previous) {
	try {
		//This function will be automatically called when this rule is processed.
		var subState = current.u_sub_state;
		var dataSources = gs.getProperty('cat.acc.datasources').toString().split(',');
		
		switch(subState.toString()) {
			case 'Initializing':
			new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().processCatalogLoad(current,dataSources[0]);
			break;
			case 'Processed Category':
			new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().processCatalogLoad(current,dataSources[1]);
			break;
			case 'Processed Catalog Item':
			new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().processCatalogLoad(current,dataSources[2]);
			break;
			case 'Processed Variable Set':
			new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().processCatalogLoad(current,dataSources[3]);
			break;
			case 'Processed Variable':
			new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().processCatalogLoad(current,dataSources[4]);
			break;
			case 'Processed Common Variable Set':
			new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().processCatalogLoad(current,dataSources[5]);
			break;
			case 'Processed Common Variable':
			new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().processCatalogLoad(current,dataSources[6]);
			break;
			case 'Processed Question Choice':
			new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().processCatalogLoad(current,dataSources[7]);
			break;
		}
	}
	catch(e) {
		gs.log('Exception in BR: Load Next Service Catalog Element, line #'+e.lineNumber+', message: '+e);
	}
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>guhann</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-07-29 12:22:06</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global                          </sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>9d7872690fe98200f59c47ace1050e46</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Load Next Service Catalog Element</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_9d7872690fe98200f59c47ace1050e46</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>guhann</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-07-30 08:34:39</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=9d7872690fe98200f59c47ace1050e46"/></record_update>

value=""/></filter_condition><message/><name>Update Catalog Load Status</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[function onAfter(current, previous) {
	try {
		//This function will be automatically called when this rule is processed.
		var subState = [];
		subState['Import Catalog Category'] = 'Processed Category';
		subState['Import Catalog Item'] = 'Processed Catalog Item';
		subState['Import Variable Set'] = 'Processed Variable Set';
		subState['Import Variable'] = 'Processed Variable';
		subState['Import Common Variable Set'] = 'Processed Common Variable Set';
		subState['Import Common Variable'] = 'Processed Common Variable';
		subState['Import Question Choice'] = 'Processed Question Choice';
		subState['Import Catalog Variable Set'] = 'Processed Catalog Variable Set';
		
		var lsc = new GlideRecord('u_load_service_catalog');
		lsc.addQuery('u_state','Pending');
		lsc.query();
		
		if(lsc.next()) {
			lsc.u_sub_state = subState[current.data_source.getDisplayValue().toString()];
			if(lsc.u_sub_state == 'Processed Catalog Variable Set') {
				lsc.u_state = 'Processed';
				//Disabling Scheduled Import Definiton after processing is complete.
				new CatalogAcceleratorUtils().disableScheduledImport();
			}
			lsc.update();
		}
	}
	catch(e) {
		gs.log('Exception in BR: Update Catalog Load Status, line #'+e.lineNumber+', message: '+e);
	}
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>guhann</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-07-29 12:13:26</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global                          </sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>9d7edea50fe98200f59c47ace1050eeb</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Update Catalog Load Status</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_9d7edea50fe98200f59c47ace1050eeb</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>guhann</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-07-30 08:36:15</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=9d7edea50fe98200f59c47ace1050eeb"/></record_update>

		//This function will be automatically called when this rule is processed.
		var gR = new GlideRecord('u_load_service_catalog');
		gR.addQuery('u_state','Pending');
		gR.query();
		
		if(gR.next()) {

			current.setAbortAction(true);
		}
	}
	catch(e) {
		gs.log('Exception in BR: Restrict Multiple Load, line #'+e.lineNumber+', message: '+e);
	}
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>guhann</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-07-29 17:07:33</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global                          </sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>563a3fed0fe98200f59c47ace1050e04</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Restrict Multiple Load</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_563a3fed0fe98200f59c47ace1050e04</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>guhann</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-07-30 08:36:24</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=563a3fed0fe98200f59c47ace1050e04"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_5bc9b1e10fe98200f59c47ace1050e6a
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.CatalogAcceleratorUtils</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>CatalogAcceleratorUtils</name><script><![CDATA[var CatalogAcceleratorUtils = Class.create();
CatalogAcceleratorUtils.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
	validateDataFile : function() {
		var id = this.getParameter('sysparm_id');
		var gR = new GlideRecord('sys_attachment');
		gR.addQuery('table_name', 'u_load_service_catalog');
		gR.addQuery('table_sys_id',id);
		gR.query();
		
		if(gR.next()) {
			return 'true';
		}
		return 'false';
	},
	
	processCatalogLoad : function(obj,dataSource) {
		var gR = new GlideRecord('sys_attachment');
		gR.addQuery('table_name', 'sys_data_source');
		gR.addQuery('table_sys_id',dataSource);
		gR.query();
		
		if(gR.next())
			gR.deleteRecord();
		
		GlideSysAttachment.copy(obj.getTableName(), obj.sys_id, 'sys_data_source', dataSource);
		this.loadCatalogElement(dataSource);
	},
	
	loadCatalogElement : function(dataSource) {
		var scheduledImport = new GlideRecord('scheduled_import_set');
		scheduledImport.addQuery('sys_id',gs.getProperty('cat.acc.sch.importset'));
		scheduledImport.query();
		
		if(scheduledImport.next()) {
			scheduledImport.data_source = dataSource;
			scheduledImport.active = 'true';
			scheduledImport.update();
			SncTriggerSynchronizer.executeNow(scheduledImport);
		}
	},
	
	disableScheduledImport : function() {
		var scheduledImport = new GlideRecord('scheduled_import_set');
		scheduledImport.addQuery('sys_id',gs.getProperty('cat.acc.sch.importset'));
		scheduledImport.query();
		
		if(scheduledImport.next()) {
			scheduledImport.data_source = '';
			scheduledImport.active = 'false';
			scheduledImport.update();
		}
		this.clearDataSourceFile();
	},
	
	//Deleting data files attached to data sources
	clearDataSourceFile : function() {
		var dataSources = gs.getProperty('cat.acc.datasources').toString().split(',');
		var dataFile;
		for(var i=0; i<dataSources.length; i++) {
			dataFile = new GlideRecord('sys_attachment');
			dataFile.addEncodedQuery('table_name=sys_data_source^table_sys_id='+dataSources[i]);
			dataFile.query();
			dataFile.deleteRecord();
		}
	},
	
	updateLoadStatus : function(obj) {
		obj.u_state = 'Processed';
		obj.update();
	},
	
	type: 'CatalogAcceleratorUtils'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>guhann</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-07-29 08:01:40</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>5bc9b1e10fe98200f59c47ace1050e6a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>17</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CatalogAcceleratorUtils</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_5bc9b1e10fe98200f59c47ace1050e6a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>guhann</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-07-30 09:50:02</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
